WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.166 --> 00:00:06.433
Did I not tell you the whereabouts of Sister Chen Lin?

2
00:00:06.566 --> 00:00:07.900
Why won't you let me go?

3
00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:14.900
Don't worry, he went to a very safe place

4
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.700
I promise you I will let you see him again

5
00:00:22.366 --> 00:00:23.233
Promise me

6
00:00:23.566 --> 00:00:26.500
Take this with you wherever you go.

7
00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:27.933
When I'm not around

8
00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:28.766
He will protect you

9
00:00:28.766 --> 00:00:30.566
I put a locator in the toy

10
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:31.933
Once the hot pot flashes

11
00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:33.900
I know where he is the first time

12
00:00:37.133 --> 00:00:39.000
Give it to Sister Chen Ning

13
00:00:41.300 --> 00:00:42.233
Why is that?

14
00:00:44.866 --> 00:00:47.000
He needs protection more than I do

15
00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:08.100
Brother Jiang Yu, are you really not coming to my house to sit?

16
00:01:08.533 --> 00:01:09.600
What do you think?

17
00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:13.000
I know Brother Jiang Yu doesn't like me

18
00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.433
But at least give it a show

19
00:01:15.533 --> 00:01:18.000
Otherwise, I know that something is really going on today.

20
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.066
OK.

21
00:01:24.133 --> 00:01:26.700
Brother, this is not me coming to you.

